These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
City: san-francisco, london, boston
1. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
2. the person traveling to boston is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the person traveling to london##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| City   | san-francisco | boston | london |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, white, aquamarine
1. the person who likes chestnut is between the person who likes white and the person who likes aquamarine##2
2. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Color   | aquamarine | chestnut | white |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, tram, quad-bike
1. the person driving the tram is between the person driving the van and the person driving the quad-bike##2
2. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Transport   | quad-bike | tram | van |

 #################################

 
