1. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is singing and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | chess | singing |

